reviewText: TRACKS INCLUDE: "Cab Calloway's Jitterbug Party"(1935); "Manhattan Merry-Go-Round"(excerpt 1937); "Blues In The Night"(1942); "Minnie The Moocher"(1942); "Virginia, Georgia & Caroline"(1942); "The Skunk Song"(1942); "I Can't Give You Anything But Love"(1950); "Minnie The Moocher"(1950); "St. James Infirmary"(1950). "These rare historical films were transferred from the original 16mm through state-of-the-art audio and digital video signal enhancers."
